ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisAppointment of SHELLY KEHOE of Port Hawkesbury, Nova Scotia, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, to hold office during pleasure, for a term of three years, or until the dissolution of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, whichever occurs first.
